Package de.ikor.sip.foundation.core.actuator.routes

Class AdapterRouteEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ikor.sip.foundation.core.actuator.routes.AdapterRouteEndpoint
  • @Component
@RestControllerEndpoint(id="adapter-routes")
public class AdapterRouteEndpoint
extends Object
    Entry point of the HTTP-only Actuator endpoint that exposes management functions from the CamelContext and Camel's JMX MBeans.

    Among other features, you can use it to list, start and stop Camel routes, as well as to get a plenty of details about each one of them.
